data.description:
Cute home on a large corner lot!  Kitchen and Bathrooms updated last year, as well as fresh paint and new flooring. HVAC and Water Heater replaced in 2021. This home has HUGE backyard that is just waiting for your garden or firepit to make it yours!
Close to great downtown restuatants and boutiques.  Refridgerator and washer and dryer are negotiable
